      <description>&lt;p&gt;I received the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.keystonesymposia.org/financial-aid/scholarships&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Keystone Symposia Future of Science Fund scholarship&lt;/a&gt; from the conference &lt;strong&gt;Keystone Symposia X1: Genomic Instability and DNA repair&lt;/strong&gt;. I&amp;rsquo;ll show our new results about rNMP incorporation characteristics in human mtDNA at this conference. Welcome to check my poster (and potential talk) in Whistler, BC, Canada on Mar 19-23!&lt;/p&gt;
