      <description>&lt;p&gt;I completed my thesis &amp;ldquo;&lt;em&gt;Revealing patterns of ribonucleotide incorporation in genomic DNA of eukaryotic cells&lt;/em&gt;&amp;rdquo;  and got my Ph.D. degree in Bioinformatics at Georgia Tech. Ph.D. program is a long journey and I&amp;rsquo;ve received plenty of help during the five years. Thanks my advisor &lt;strong&gt;Dr. Francesca Storici&lt;/strong&gt; for all her guidance and my committee members &lt;strong&gt;Dr. Mark Borodovsky&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Dr. Shamkant Navathe&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Dr. Patrick McGrath&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Dr. Fredrik Vannberg&lt;/strong&gt; for all their support! After graduation, I&amp;rsquo;ll continue my research in Storici Lab as a postdoc. Hope I can do some better research on rNMP incorporation in DNA!&lt;/p&gt;
